## WorkerOptions.vmRedirectPorts property

Set of ports in the virtual machine to make available from the host machine. It should include [vmPlaywrightPort](./assistive-playwright-test.workeroptions.vmplaywrightport.md)<!-- -->. Defaults to an array containing only [vmPlaywrightPort](./assistive-playwright-test.workeroptions.vmplaywrightport.md)<!-- -->.
